                "invention-title": [
                    "Energy storage scale optimization configuration method of off-grid renewable energy hydrogen production system",
                    "一种离网型可再生能源制氢系统的储能规模优化配置方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides an energy storage scale optimization configuration method of an off-grid renewable energy hydrogen production system. The method comprises the steps of obtaining a historical operation curve of renewable energy of a target area; constructing a boundary curve library based on the historical operation curve; obtaining a preset objective function and a constraint condition, and constructing an energy storage optimal configuration model of the off-grid renewable energy hydrogen production system with the maximum hydrogen production amount as a target based on the objective function and the constraint condition; configuring input parameters of the energy storage optimal configuration model; determining a target input parameter based on the boundary curve library, and performing energy storage scale optimization calculation based on the target input parameter and the energy storage optimization configuration model to obtain an energy storage utilization scale for each curve in the boundary curve library; and obtaining the energy storage configuration scale of the off-grid renewable energy hydrogen production system based on the energy storage utilization scale. The operation characteristics of renewable energy sources, the operation requirements of the hydrogen production system and the economical efficiency of the energy storage equipment can be comprehensively considered, and the economical efficiency and the operation efficiency of the system are comprehensively improved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本申请提出一种离网型可再生能源制氢系统的储能规模优化配置方法，包括：获取目标地区可再生能源的历史运行曲线；基于历史运行曲线构建边界曲线库；获取预设的目标函数及约束条件，基于目标函数和约束条件构建以最大制氢量为目标的离网型可再生能源制氢系统的储能优化配置模型；对储能优化配置模型的输入参数进行配置；基于边界曲线库确定目标输入参数，基于目标输入参数和储能优化配置模型进行储能规模优化计算，得到针对边界曲线库中每个曲线的储能利用规模；基于储能利用规模获取离网型可再生能源制氢系统的储能配置规模。本申请能够综合考虑可再生能源的运行特点、制氢系统的运行需求以及储能设备的经济性，全面提升系统的经济性和运行效率。"
                }
            ]
